    {
      "id": "node-instance-contract-input",
      "type": "input",
      "label": "Input",
      "position": {
        "x": 3644.2797978692142,
        "y": 405
      },
      "width": 360,
      "height": 240,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "title": "Input",
        "body": "A node instance carries semantic node data plus binding metadata that points back to the class authority responsible for its defaults, views, meaning, and renderer behavior. It may be content-bearing, boundary-oriented, infrastructural, interactive, or some composition of those roles; content-hosting is optional rather than universal. It also carries the on-disk declaration/root-plus-fragments shape: one `root.node`, any connected fragments, explicit fragment declaration by a type node of type `fragment`, legal fragment adjacency, whether the artifact is single-file or multi-file under that shape, runtime-root discovery behavior when `root.node` is absent, single-root ownership of fragments, and ports exposed on `root.node` only. Zoom or host selection may change which representation is shown, but not what node instance it is.",
        "body": "A node instance carries semantic node data plus binding metadata that points back to the class authority responsible for its defaults, views, meaning, and renderer behavior. It may be content-bearing, boundary-oriented, infrastructural, interactive, or some composition of those roles; content-hosting is optional rather than universal. It also carries the on-disk declaration/root-plus-fragments shape: one `root.node`, any connected fragments, explicit fragment declaration by a type node of type `fragment`, legal fragment adjacency, whether the artifact is single-file or multi-file under that shape, runtime-root discovery behavior when `root.node` is absent, single-root ownership of fragments, and ports exposed on `root.node` only. Zoom or host selection may change which representation is shown, but not what node instance it is.",
        "required": true,
        "_classBinding": {
